        "  - Run 'Firefox Nightly Profile Manager', choose 'Scoop-Nightly' then click 'Start Nightly'.",
        "  - Visit 'about:profiles' page in Firefox Nightly to check *DEFAULT* profile.",
        "For details: https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/profile-manager-create-remove-switch-firefox-profiles"
    ],
    "architecture": {
        "64bit": {
            "url": "https://archive.mozilla.org/pub/firefox/nightly/2026/04/2026-04-19-20-35-36-mozilla-central/firefox-151.0a1.en-US.win64.installer.exe#/dl.7z",
            "hash": "sha512:37cfba72e62a34c034ec85f11b298e5b9982d86ba0af1a2d6ddfaa029aaed5d863dd5a52d67b55060ec3d195ddd8acf709d1523d12634ab11f72bc4e9cae7b21"
        },
        "32bit": {
            "url": "https://archive.mozilla.org/pub/firefox/nightly/2026/04/2026-04-19-20-35-36-mozilla-central/firefox-151.0a1.en-US.win32.installer.exe#/dl.7z",
